data.description: Lovely Single Family Home in Waterview; 4 bedrooms, 3 full bath, and 2 car garage. This house has a great floor plan, and all the rooms are well proportional. Right when you step in you will see a spacious living room and dining area combo. The Kitchen has 42" cabinets, breakfast bar overlooks family room. The Master bedroom suite on the first floor has a huge walk-in closet, and adjoining bathroom with garden tub, separate stall shower and double sinks. Two other bedrooms, bonus room, and full bath are also located on first floor. Upstairs has a large Master bedroom with sitting room, huge walking closet, and full bathroom. Relax or entertain on covered porch overlooking huge peaceful, fully fenced, backyard which has plenty of space for family activities or a pool (One of the biggest lots in the community). Community has pool with poolside cabanas, playground, biking and walking trails. Minutes away from schools, shopping, entertainment, Florida theme parks, and downtown Orlando. Approximately 1 mile from the new Sun Rail Station. DO NOT FORGET TO CLICK ON THE VIRTUAL TOUR.
